# Reference Modelfile. Stage 08 (08_export.py) GENERATES a real one at
# data/model/Modelfile with the correct FROM path and your persona from config.yaml.
# This copy documents the shape and lets you tweak params by hand if you want.

FROM ./data/model/gguf/model.gguf

# Persona — keep it short. " /no_think" disables Qwen3 reasoning so it answers
# directly with a tweet instead of emitting <think> blocks.
SYSTEM """You are your_handle, replying on X. Be concise, opinionated, and in your own voice. /no_think"""

PARAMETER temperature 0.8
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
